edu.harvard.cga.gtools.tekml
Class AttributeTable

java.lang.Object
  edu.harvard.cga.gtools.tekml.AttributeTable

public class AttributeTable
extends java.lang.Object

A simple java bean that encapsulates data from actual attribute table from KML file that contains only the name value pairs that correspond to allowable items specified in the config. Note these are just unvalidated string values. In the current implementation, the items selected are time values and name The parsing and other complexities and business rules of the time values are handled by the TimeSource and KmlTimeData classes after the raw data strings are passed to them. Objects of this class are created by a factory method in another class

Author:
W.Hays (whays at nearity.com)
